133
00:13:40,477 --> 00:13:43,503
<font color="yellow">And that seems to help you too.</font>

134
00:13:43,503 --> 00:13:44,974
<font color="yellow">I told you to mind your own business.</font>

135
00:13:44,974 --> 00:13:49,007
<font color="yellow">I've already found out about all this,
