136
00:13:49,007 --> 00:13:50,147
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

137
00:13:52,070 --> 00:13:54,166
<font color="yellow">would like to help you.</font>

138
00:14:48,925 --> 00:14:51,435
<font color="yellow"><i>Your Highness.</i></font>

139
00:14:51,435 --> 00:14:54,748
<font color="yellow">There is an unfortunate rumor
