140
00:14:54,748 --> 00:14:58,388
<font color="yellow">the Red Gentleman's Robe is still alive.</font>

141
00:14:58,388 --> 00:15:01,194
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

142
00:15:01,194 --> 00:15:04,998
