145
00:15:13,729 --> 00:15:16,355
<font color="yellow">Is that it?</font>

146
00:15:16,355 --> 00:15:19,174
<font color="yellow">- That's not it...
- Then what is it?</font>

147
00:15:23,945 --> 00:15:27,994
<font color="yellow">Find the source of this preposterous
