233
00:22:52,856 --> 00:22:54,778
<font color="yellow">Why are you...</font>

234
00:22:57,211 --> 00:22:58,908
<font color="yellow">Why are you drinking that?</font>

235
00:23:07,576 --> 00:23:10,115
<font color="yellow">What are you doing right now?</font>

236
00:23:10,115 --> 00:23:12,825
<font color="yellow">Where are you going
