00:25:33,274 --> 00:25:35,245
<font color="yellow">Hey. Ma Soon Deuk.</font>

273
00:25:39,465 --> 00:25:41,159
<font color="yellow">Let go of me!</font>

274
00:25:41,955 --> 00:25:44,988
<font color="yellow">Let go! Let me go!</font>

275
00:25:44,988 --> 00:25:46,401
<font color="yellow">Let go of me!</font>

276
00:25:49,192 --> 00:25:50,840
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

277
00:25:53,354 --> 00:25:56,914
<font color="yellow">What are you doing
