278
00:25:56,914 --> 00:25:58,476
<font color="yellow">Politely.</font>

279
00:25:58,476 --> 00:25:59,751
<font color="yellow">Soon Deuk.</font>

280
00:26:00,973 --> 00:26:04,823
<font color="yellow">Where's Heo Joon? Hm?</font>

281
00:26:04,823 --> 00:26:08,363
<font color="yellow">- I don't know.
