285
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:19,351
<font color="yellow">Tell me where he is.</font>

286
00:26:19,351 --> 00:26:20,922
<font color="yellow">Where is he? Tell me.</font>

287
00:26:22,268 --> 00:26:24,438
<font color="yellow">I can't tell you what I don't know.</font>

288
00:26:24,438 --> 00:26:28,346
<font color="yellow">He went his way.
