289
00:26:37,340 --> 00:26:40,912
<font color="yellow">You guys are trying to screw me over.</font>

290
00:26:41,603 --> 00:26:42,807
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

291
00:26:44,256 --> 00:26:46,009
