00:31:24,665 --> 00:31:26,746
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

337
00:31:32,911 --> 00:31:34,841
<font color="yellow">Stay here for a while.</font>

338
00:32:16,113 --> 00:32:17,710
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

339
00:32:40,830 --> 00:32:42,095
<font color="yellow">Follow me.</font>

